Southwestern Bell Corp said it will filerevisions with the public Utility Commission for its Dial 976Information Delivery Service.    The service, available in four Texas cities since November1986, allows customers to access sponsor-provided messages bydialing numbers that begin with 976.    Southwestern Bell said customer concerns center on the needfor restricting access to adult entertainment messages and forgreater awareness that charges apply for calls to 976 numbers.    It said its revisions are responsive to these concerns. Reuter&#3;